@HabitTracker.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:5001
# For HTTPS locally run with: dotnet run --launch-profile https
# For Docker: https://localhost:5001

### Health Check
GET {{HabitTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Get Habits
GET {{HabitTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/habits/
Accept: application/json